==制作==
===历史背景===
[[File:Warsaw_zoo_elephant_1938.jpg|thumb]]

影片改编自[[黛安·艾克曼|黛安·艾克曼]]{{tsl|en|The Zookeeper's Wife|动物园长的夫人 (小说)|同名纪实文学}}，该作品根据安东尼娜·扎宾斯卡的日记整理而成，于1968年以《人与动物》（{{lang|pl|Ludzie i zwierzęta}}）的名义出版。在历史背景的关键方面，剧本忠实于共同在{{tsl|en|Warsaw Zoo|华沙动物园}}工作的安东尼娜与丈夫扬的经历。动物园是萨宾斯基一家生活的一部分，而空袭过后华沙所遭受的破坏及其后动物园被抢劫的过程都被很好的记录下来。卢玆·赫克和他的动物繁殖实验也有历史记载，但女主人公安东尼娜和反派赫克之间的感情关系是被夸大了。萨宾斯基的后裔理查德和特蕾莎也为影片提供指导意见，其中特蕾莎在片尾演职员表中有名字<ref name="History">{{cite web |url=http://www.historyvshollywood.com/reelfaces/zookeepers-wife/ |title=The Zookeeper's Wife Movie vs the True Story of Antonina Zabinski |website=History vs Hollywood |access-date=2017-04-01 |archive-date=2017-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402082041/http://www.historyvshollywood.com/reelfaces/zookeepers-wife/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===开发===
2010年9月，消息指安琪拉·沃克曼正改编黛安·艾克曼的纪实文学《动物园长的夫人》<ref>{{cite web |url=https://movieweb.com/angela-workman-adapting-the-zookeepers-wife/ |title=Angela Workman Adapting The Zookeeper's Wife |last=Orange |first=Bradford Alan |date=2010-09-22 |website=MovieWeb |access-date=2018-03-01 |archive-date=2018-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302163927/https://movieweb.com/angela-workman-adapting-the-zookeepers-wife/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年4月30日，[[杰西卡·查斯坦|杰西卡·查斯坦]]宣布饰演主角安东尼娜，同时[[妮基·卡罗|妮基·卡罗]]签约出任导演<ref name="April2013THR">{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jessica-chastain-attached-star-zookeepers-449210 |title=Jessica Chastain Attached to Star in 'The Zookeeper's Wife' (Exclusive) |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=2013-04-30 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2018-03-01 |archive-date=2018-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107061452/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jessica-chastain-attached-star-zookeepers-449210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年8月24日，[[焦点影业|焦点影业]]买下影片美国发行权，[[丹尼爾·布爾|丹尼爾·布爾]]和{{tsl|en|Johan Heldenbergh|约翰·赫尔登伯格}}加盟剧组<ref name="Aug2015TW">{{cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/daniel-bruhl-to-star-in-the-zookeepers-wife-with-jessica-chastain-exclusive/ |title=Daniel Bruhl to Star in 'The Zookeeper’s Wife' With Jessica Chastain (Exclusive) |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |date=2015-08-14 |website=The Wrap |access-date=2018-03-01 |archive-date=2018-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302103925/https://www.thewrap.com/daniel-bruhl-to-star-in-the-zookeepers-wife-with-jessica-chastain-exclusive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

