/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2019-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929130300/https://variety.com/2017/film/global/deauville-film-festival-unveils-lineup-doug-limans-american-made-set-to-open-festival-1202535286/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

