==评价==
===票房===
影片北美票房1760万美元，海外票房860万美元，全球票房共计2610万美元，成功收回2000万美元的制片成本<ref name=BOM/>。北美方面，影片上映首周末登陆541家影院（场均6191美元），位列票房榜第10位<ref>{{cite web |last1=D'Alessandro |first1=Anthony |title=‘Boss Baby’ Bullies ‘Beast’ With $50M+ Opening; ‘Ghost’ Shell-Shocked With Low $18.6M |url=https://deadline.com/2017/04/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |website=Deadline.com |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-04-02 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814123403/https://deadline.com/2017/04/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，次周、三周和四周均为票房成绩最高的独立电影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/highest-grossing-indie-films-2017-1201764229/|title=The 20 Highest Grossing Indies of 2017 (A Running List)|first=Kate|last=Erbland|publisher=IndieWire|accessdate=2017-04-30|archive-date=2017-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170429055007/http://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/highest-grossing-indie-films-2017-1201764229/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

上映第五周，影片仍为2017年最卖座的特种片。[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]赞赏了影片的发行策略，称“[[焦点影业|焦点]]积极推动这部[[杰西卡·查斯坦|杰西卡·查斯坦]]出演的犹太人营救行动电影，创下自颁奖季以来针对特定受众群体发行电影中的最高成绩。影片没有拿下两年前《[[名畫的控訴|名畫的控訴]]》的成绩（3300万美元），比起两部电影之间的差异，这个结果更像是整体票房急剧下滑及眼下竞争影片较多所导致的”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/arthouse-audit-box-office-openers-ethnic-the-circle-1201810799/|title=Arthouse Box Office: Niche Ethnic Releases Overpower Specialty Openers|first=Tom|last=Brueggemann|website=IndieWire|accessdate=2020-09-06|archive-date=2018-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816105050/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/arthouse-audit-box-office-openers-ethnic-the-circle-1201810799/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。上映第八、九周，影片位列2017年特种片票房第三位，尽管放映场次有所减少<ref>{{cite web |last1=Erbland |first1=Kate |title=The 20 Highest Grossing Indies of 2017 (Final List) |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2017/05/highest-grossing-indie-films-2017-1201764229/ |website=IndieWire |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-07-06 |archive-date=2017-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602143302/http://www.indiewire.com/2017/05/highest-grossing-indie-films-2017-1201764229/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Zookeeper's Wife |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2994636289/ |website=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2020-09-07 |archive-date=2020-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615082220/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2994636289/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。上映第十周，IndieWire表示影片“一直是今年春季难得耀眼的作品”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Brueggemann |first1=Tom |title=‘Wonder Woman’ Sends Indie Box Office Straight to Hades |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2017/06/box-office-specialty-indie-3-idiotas-churchill-bandaid-arthouse-1201836769/ |website=IndieWire |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-06-04 |archive-date=2020-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313050536/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/06/box-office-specialty-indie-3-idiotas-churchill-bandaid-arthouse-1201836769/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===专业评价===
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]搜集了177条评论，打出了64%的新鲜度。网站共识写道：“《动物园长的夫人》有高尚的意图，但最终无法以应有的影响力将片中改编自现实的故事变为现实<ref>{{cite web |title=The Zookeeper's Wife (2017) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_zookeepers_wife_2017 |website=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Fandango |accessdate=2020-09-07 |archive-date=2017-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322111437/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_zookeepers_wife_2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据36条评论打出57/100的评分，表示“褒贬不一或口碑平平”<ref>{{cite web |title=The Zookeeper's Wife |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-zookeepers-wife |website=Metacritic |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2020-09-07 |archive-date=2018-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213214813/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-zookeepers-wife |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|PostTrak|PostTrak}}指90%的观众给出“优秀”或“非常好”的评价<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2017/04/jessica-chastain-zookeepers-wife-debut-david-lynch-documentary-specialty-box-office-1202058514/ |title=’The Zookeeper’s Wife’ Debuts To $3.3M; ‘David Lynch’ Doc Gets Solid Start – Specialty Box Office |website=Deadline Hollywood |publisher=Penske Business Media |date=2017-04-02 |first=Brian |last=Brooks |accessdate=2018-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711224250/https://deadline.com/2017/04/jessica-chastain-zookeepers-wife-debut-david-lynch-documentary-specialty-box-office-1202058514/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]将影片列入年度最佳独立电影候选名单，指“妮基·卡罗的真实故事改编历史剧情片是一部最令人心碎的影片，杰西卡·查斯坦低调的表演及一连串令人费解的戏剧性转折的相互作用下，就连心肠最坚硬的人也会泪流满面”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kohn |first1=Eric |last2=Ehrlich |first2=David |last3=Thompson |first3=Anne |last4=Erbland |first4=Kate |title=The 17 Best Indie Movies of 2017 (So Far) |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2017/07/best-indie-movies-2017-so-far-get-out-the-big-sick-1201849542/ |website=IndieWire |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-07-04 |archive-date=2019-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416103758/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/07/best-indie-movies-2017-so-far-get-out-the-big-sick-1201849542/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的{{tsl|en|Mick LaSalle|米克·拉萨尔}}给出5星满分好评，认为影片“从一开始就抓住了我们”：“《动物园长的夫人》并非通过描绘宏大动作场面来呈现壮阔感，而是专注于情感的转变和闪光点。战争是非常重大的外部事件，但卡罗提醒着我们，艰难度过战争的人类和动物也在内心经历着一场战争<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/The-Zookeeper-s-Wife-World-War-II-11036397.php|title='Zookeeper’s Wife' — World War II from inside Warsaw Zoo|last=LaSelle|first=Mick|date=2017-03-30|website=SFGate|access-date=2017-05-19|archive-date=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518234538/http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/The-Zookeeper-s-Wife-World-War-II-11036397.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的肯尼斯·杜兰（Kenneth Turan）认为，“妮基·卡罗和杰西卡·查斯坦打造了情感上令人满足的《动物园长的夫人》<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-zookeepers-wife-review-20170330-story.html|title=Niki Caro and Jessica Chastain create an emotionally satisfying 'Zookeeper's Wife'|last=Turan|first=Kenneth|date=2017-03-30|website=LA Times|access-date=2017-05-19|archive-date=2017-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519114608/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-zookeepers-wife-review-20170330-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[美联社|美联社]]指出，影片“讲述了一个引人入胜的真实战争”，“既激励人心，也在这个风云诡谲的年代提醒着大家，即便面对令人惊讶的邪恶威胁，人性和善良也可乘势崛起<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bahr |first1=Lindsey |title=Review: 'The Zookeeper's Wife' tells a riveting true story |url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/69da883a3b65413ca35be24e5643deeb/review-zookeepers-wife-tells-riveting-true-story |website=AP News |accessdate=2020-09-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415200624/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/69da883a3b65413ca35be24e5643deeb/review-zookeepers-wife-tells-riveting-true-story |archivedate=2017-04-15 |date=2017-03-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”《[[新共和|新共和]]》的雅各布·索尔将影片标榜为“首部女权主义犹太人大屠杀电影”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Soll |first1=Jacob |title=The Revelatory Horror of The Zookeeper’s Wife |url=https://newrepublic.com/article/141806/revelatory-horror-zookeepers-wife |website=The New Republic |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519051706/https://newrepublic.com/article/141806/revelatory-horror-zookeepers-wife |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的彼得·德布鲁格（Peter Debruge）并不认同这部影片：“眼下似乎没有更好的处理办法，但不幸的是，《动物园长的夫人》对人类戏剧的呈现，还不及片中动物的遭遇令人感兴趣。而动物给我们种族造成的危害，和犹太人大屠杀有过之而无不及，对于这样的主题，影片的缺点可谓不小<ref>{{cite web |last1=Deburge |first1=Peter |title=Film Review: ‘The Zookeeper’s Wife’ |url=https://variety.com/2017/film/reviews/the-zookeepers-wife-review-jessica-chastain-1202011801/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-03-20 |archive-date=2020-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608111832/https://variety.com/2017/film/reviews/the-zookeepers-wife-review-jessica-chastain-1202011801/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”然而，《综艺》的克里斯托弗·塔普利（Kristopher Tapley）却认为影片值得参与奥斯卡奖角逐<ref>{{cite web |last1=Tapley |first1=Kristopher |title=Midway Oscars Forecast: A Cluttered Landscape for Indies and Streamers |url=https://variety.com/2017/film/in-contention/midway-oscars-forecast-indies-streaming-platforms-1202477799/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-06-29 |archive-date=2019-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215172054/https://variety.com/2017/film/in-contention/midway-oscars-forecast-indies-streaming-platforms-1202477799/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的斯蒂芬·霍尔登（Stephen Holden）认为影片是“宠物版《[[辛德勒的名单|辛德勒的名单]]》”，“过于胆怯、经过消毒，对儿童绝对安全”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Holden |first1=Stephen |title=Review: In ‘The Zookeeper’s Wife,’ the Holocaust Seems Tame |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/29/movies/the-zookeepers-wife-review-jessica-chastain.html |website=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-03-29 |archive-date=2017-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330013302/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/29/movies/the-zookeepers-wife-review-jessica-chastain.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

波兰的影评人非常认可这部替他们的历史说话的电影。《克拉科夫邮报》表示：“无论什么时候，普天下的电影都在祈祷理智及慈善、同情及人性的文明价值观，而这种价值理念正被威胁着要给群体精神失常、仇恨及野蛮所统治。从新近历史中的这段最黑暗时期得出的教训永远不会过时<ref>{{cite web |last1=Karski |first1=Michal |title=Film Review: The Zookeeper’s Wife |url=http://www.krakowpost.com/14750/2017/08/review-zookeepers-wife-film |website=The Kralow Post |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-08-08 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728000132/http://www.krakowpost.com/14750/2017/08/review-zookeepers-wife-film |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

《女性变革之声》（''Women's Voices For Change''）的亚历山德拉·麦卡伦（Alexandra Macaaron）盛赞影片，指“《动物园长的夫人》是少见的犹太人大屠杀题材影片，以女性视角看待战争，讲述女性竭力保护每一个活着的生灵、陌生人及朋友的故事”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Macaaron |first1=Alexandra |title=‘The Zookeeper's Wife’— An Extraordinary True Story Of Humanity |url=https://womensvoicesforchange.org/the-zookeepers-wife-an-extraordinary-true-story-of-humanity.htm |website=Women's Voices for Change |accessdate=2020-09-07 |date=2017-04-18 |archive-date=2017-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220131346/https://womensvoicesforchange.org/the-zookeepers-wife-an-extraordinary-true-story-of-humanity.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

